description: A crew of halflings is building a house off to the side of the road, filling the air with banging and cheerful banter.  You are forced to step over the boards and buckets of nails that line the street and you must constantly shake wood shavings from your hair.  Examining the chaos the building has created, you briefly wonder how anything gets done here.

Evidence that a crew is building a house off to the side of the road lies strewn about.  You are forced to step over the boards and buckets of nails that line the street and the smell of wood shavings fills the air.  Examining the chaos the building has created, you briefly wonder how anything gets done here.
title: [Temple Burrow, Cholen Lane]
